race.description: Mental Health /Breast Cancer Awareness Month Hcp (Bm58)
race.comment: HEADLINE LEGEND (6) didn't do a bad job when fourth last start over 1100m at Warwick, beaten 2.25 lengths. That followed a win at this track the start prior. Well placed and there is no reason why he cannot make amends. FAST FUSION (1) gets a change of rider and has been freshened up since finishing sixth over 1100m at Gold Coast Poly last start. Can feature prominently. I'LLTELLYOUSO (2) strips fitter second-up from the spell and gets 3kg weight relief from the low draw. Ticks a few boxes. The well-related DON'T BE DRAMATIC (5) (half to Listed winner and 2xG3 placed Danny's St Darci) best of the rest.
